H0.text: Porcupine grass is also known as what. Pampas Grass

H1.text: Porcupine grass is also known as what. Buffalo Grass

H2.text: Porcupine grass is also known as what. Blue Grama

H3.text: Porcupine grass is also known as what. Susuki

A4.text: Porcupine grass refers to Miscanthus sinensis, Stipa spartea, and Triodia species.

A5.text: Miscanthus sinensis is native to eastern Asia

A6.text: Triodia species (such as Triodia scariosa and Triodia irritans) are native to Australia
